                "caption": "Figure 3:Guidance.We compute the reference displacement by processing cross-frame attentions with an argmax operation and rearranging them into displacement maps, identifying patch-aware cross-frame relationships. For video synthesis, we do the same operation with a soft argmax to preserve gradients, and impose reconstruction with the reference displacement.",
